title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: When trying to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight/map.
EB: The export process should complete without encountering any exceptions.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export data from a table that contains a highlight/map.
3. Observe the exception being thrown.
